name: WestJet Airlines SOLD for $5 Billion to Onex Corporation
description:
Earlier today, it was announced that WestJet, Calgary's hometown airline, had been sold to a private equity firm based in Toronto for 5 billion dollars. Here's my take on the situation and what it means for WestJet customers right now.
